<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="485">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="485">The publication lists seven female paratypes with the same collecting information in the Natal Museum (now KwaZulu-Natal Museum - NMSA) collection. No paratypes of this species were found in the collection. There are only two other specimens of this species in the collection also from the Humansdorp area from 1965. The holotype is in good condition.</paragraph>
